Package com.opengamma.strata.collect.id Description

Identifier and link data structures.

This package provides a standard identifier and link mechanism.

The identifier is used to uniquely identify domain objects. Each identifier consists of two parts, a scheme and a value that is unique within that scheme.

The link is used to connect two identified domain objects together. This provides loose coupling between different parts of the object model.
